      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can u help me with a section that tackles the counter-arguments? some people argue that a meritocracy is more important and that redistribution is basically unfair to those who worked hard to earn their wealth. how should i frame their view so it looks like a weak or illogical argument compared to the social justice side?",
